{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2031","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"李宗豪市政總質詢","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2031-1.jpeg","sequence":2031,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/i12ff2QeKi95qn67/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-05-28T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"李宗豪市政總質詢"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪市政總質詢"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這次的總質詢，準備太多沒有講完，列出重點向大家報告 🔜"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"教育資源"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"📌 教育資源"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山就學人口快速成長，但教育資源供不應求，硬體設施也不完善，我提醒教育局，提前準備因應未來可能會有爆炸性就學需求！我具體建議："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 文青國中小二期、活動中心應盡快發包開工。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 大崗高中應提前規劃，成立設校籌備處。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 尋找閒置公有地設立托嬰中心、幼兒園。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 幸福國中操場工程應加速進度。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 大坪頂地區缺乏圖書館，呼籲市府規劃一座兒童圖書館，結合周邊公園綠地，打造開放式兒童文學基地！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"交通及建設"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"📌 交通及建設"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▪️ 道路建設加速：變一道路、長慶一街瓶頸打通、青山路接文化一路、牛角坡路接樂善一路等。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 盡快補足公車司機人力，完整大眾運輸路網。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 棕線捷運核定通過，要求加速後續進度，爭取明年動工！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 要求恢復棕線捷運 BRH05A 龍壽站，平衡區域發展。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 要求提高捷運聯開容積，提升公共效益。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 龜山國民運動中心已流標多次，要求今年發包動工！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 爭取提供棒球員完善的室內打擊練習場！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 鐵路地下化後，建議市府參考綠廊道方式，連結龜山桃林步道，規劃帶狀公園。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"宜居環境"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"📌 宜居環境"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山人口成長率第一名，許多公共建設卻不完善，不合時宜的設施也應該檢討，我要求市府重視鄉親居住的環境。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 增加垃圾車、增加清潔隊員人力、調整清運路線。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n▪️ 要求大埔垃圾轉運站退場！還給鄉親乾淨的居住環境！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n市長及副市長承諾轉運站於今年底退場‼️"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2031-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2031-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"李宗豪市政總質詢","depth":2,"text":"李宗豪市政總質詢","children":[{"id":"教育資源","depth":3,"text":"📌 教育資源"},{"id":"交通及建設","depth":3,"text":"📌 交通及建設"},{"id":"宜居環境","depth":3,"text":"📌 宜居環境"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2031.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2031.md","_extension":"md"}